name: Wifedoge
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: Wifedoge is a good wife who can help doge make money. She starts to make money for you automatically when you hold wifedoge. At the same time, there is a punishment mechanism for those who abandon her. She will give you rewards for staying true to her.
